      "text": "……ん？\n雫、あっちですみれが呼んでるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh?\nShizuku‚ Sumire is calling you over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.2999953985,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
