    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ、見たよ\n今返事をしようと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I saw it.\nI was just about to reply…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.8666559617,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03-szk014.m4a",
      "text": "みんな今日は、特に……可愛い……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone looks particularly… cute today…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 126.2133267212,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03-szk015.m4a",
      "text": "もう、ステージじゃないから\n写真……撮り放題……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since it's not on stage anymore‚\nWe can… take as many photos as we want…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.6000025194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03-szk016.m4a",
      "text": "ファンサが手厚い……最高のイベント……！\n尊過ぎて、さとみさんと撮りまくってる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I like their gorgeous fan-friendly things… It's the best event…!\nIt's so precious that I've been taking tons of photos with Satomi-san…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9666752896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03/sud_vo_adv_card_szk_05_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "同じユニットの打ち上げだろ……\nドルオタのスイッチが入ってるぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's just a unit after-party…\nShe's turning into idol fan mode.",
